# Machine Loan Manager

A lightweight web application to track machine loans, reservations,
and overdue alerts for IT teams and equipment management.

## Features
- Add machines
- Track machine loans
- Equipment reservation
- Overdue alerts
- Simple dashboard

## Tech Stack
- Node.js
- Express
- SQLite

## Installation

git clone https://github.com/yourname/machine-loan-manager
cd machine-loan-manager
npm install
npm start

Open http://localhost:3000
